{"tid":1942653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"\"废青”“背叛华夏民族”、中共赶快收拾“曱甴”——马来西亚人爱“祖国”","createTime":"2020-03-25T08:08:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T10:34:37.000Z","uid":334191,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"593c376368ad32ec192448a01123e9df367139d4","tid":1942653,"uid":334191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:08:09.000Z","msg":"本来没我什么事儿，但我不巧回了一句楼主不代表马来西亚，然后就被他人肉，连原帖也改了，特别加入了本&ldquo;曱甴&rdquo;的大头照。3小时内114次转载。<br />\n<br />\n所以我把原帖截图，并节选了一部分评论一起翻译（时间太紧，可润色之处不少）。为了平衡起见，也收录了两位马来西亚人的反驳。同时把收录的评论根据内容分类重排。<br />\n<br />\n截图里还有其他精彩内容，请大家慢慢观赏。<br />\n<br />\n实在没有精力再做马来文版，但马来西亚通行英语，所以也不用另作，把这些截图直接贴到英语和马来语群组，一并贴到连登。<br />\n<br />\n根据1948年煽动法令，共产主义宣传与仇恨言论在马来西亚均属于刑事罪，但为了尊重言论自由起见，我并没有把他们举报到Polis Diraja.<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ET7oKbUUMAAiLwl?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FET7oKbUUMAAiLwl%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dorig&h=fccac2db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ET7oM0qUwAIlFK5?format=png&amp;name=orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FET7oM0qUwAIlFK5%3Fformat%3Dpng%26name%3Dorig&h=c779e197&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ET7oOTIUUAEGleP?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FET7oOTIUUAEGleP%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dorig&h=639e8683&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/ET7oPh5U4AAhdnA?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FET7oPh5U4AAhdnA%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dorig&h=c7719a64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5db7e0819d9aca85b9eaa2afd741e22df3b71c33","tid":1942653,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:09:02.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8ecf8b50519cf7ab44d2d923b7637ea3a2329d18","tid":1942653,"uid":150483,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:11:47.000Z","msg":"嘩好嬲啊<br />\n<br />\n正式打馬拉狗<br />\n成日話咩都唔關你事，宜家就比個回力鏢你開波"},{"pid":"36405c40f540da2ba8ea9f7081cf82d77f12b925","tid":1942653,"uid":334191,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:12:34.000Z","msg":"说明：被人肉的Sulaiman Gu 就是本人。因为我的脸书头像正好是&ldquo;光复香港时代革命&rdquo;衬衫，所以被他当作&ldquo;曱甴&rdquo;的标本。然后他们又搜出我的其他讯息，包括以前接受美国之音采访，还有在中国的时候和同学一起庆祝开斋节的照片。"},{"pid":"ca62f9ccfddb60775807c9646a151b9cd7d870c6","tid":1942653,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"36405c40f540da2ba8ea9f7081cf82d77f12b925","tid":1942653,"uid":334191,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:12:34.000Z","msg":"说明：被人肉的Sulaiman Gu 就是本人。因为我的脸书头像正好是&ldquo;光复香港时代革命&rdquo;衬衫，所以被他当作&ldquo;曱甴&rdquo;的标本。然后他们又搜出我的其他讯息，包括以前接受美国之音采访，还有在中国的时候和同学一起庆祝开斋节的照片。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:13:29.000Z","msg":"什麼?!"},{"pid":"096f860ff71ab66b0113f7e0745c9f82aa27938a","tid":1942653,"uid":258770,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:15:12.000Z","msg":"難得有反共法就舉報吧"},{"pid":"a10d884f4f8f20e79937134fddd37f27acc5a115","tid":1942653,"uid":334191,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca62f9ccfddb60775807c9646a151b9cd7d870c6","tid":1942653,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"36405c40f540da2ba8ea9f7081cf82d77f12b925","tid":1942653,"uid":334191,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:12:34.000Z","msg":"说明：被人肉的Sulaiman Gu 就是本人。因为我的脸书头像正好是&ldquo;光复香港时代革命&rdquo;衬衫，所以被他当作&ldquo;曱甴&rdquo;的标本。然后他们又搜出我的其他讯息，包括以前接受美国之音采访，还有在中国的时候和同学一起庆祝开斋节的照片。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:13:29.000Z","msg":"什麼?!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:17:17.000Z","msg":"突然发现我在这里的用户名和脸书名不一样，解释一下事情的前因后果。"},{"pid":"0bc24fbbc7ce23a62776892645473927d3657ca4","tid":1942653,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T08:19:45.000Z","msg":"支持大馬手足<img src=\"/assets/